    <p><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-1a' );" name="003-1a" class="pb">[003-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　禹貢指南卷三</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:219'>　　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　毛晃　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:242'>導岍及岐至于荆山逾于河壺口雷首至于太岳厎柱</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='242:261'>析城至于王屋太行恒山至于碣石入于海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='261:284'>　導山　岍山　在右扶風即呉嶽也　周禮大司樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='284:307'>　注五嶽岱在兗州衡在荆州嵩在豫州華在雍州恒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='307:330'>　在并州　正義曰周處鎬京在五嶽外故鄭康成注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='330:356'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-1b' );" name="003-1b" class="pb">[003-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='356:379'>　康誥云岐鎬處五嶽之外周公為其道里不均故東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='379:402'>　營洛邑合諸侯謀作天子之居是西都無西嶽權立</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='402:425'>　呉嶽為西嶽　廣雅河西曰嶽頂有五峰　周禮職</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='425:448'>　方氏雍州其山鎮曰嶽山注嶽呉嶽也　漢地理志</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='448:471'>　呉嶽在汧縣西古文謂之汧山秦都咸陽山曰西嶽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='471:481'>　岐山　解在雍州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='481:491'>　荆山　解在雍州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='491:514'>　壺口山　水經壺口山在河東北屈縣東南　馮衍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='514:540'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-2a' );" name="003-2a" class="pb">[003-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='540:563'>　顯志賦瞰太行之嵯峩兮觀壺口之崢嶸注太行山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='563:586'>　在上黨南壺口山在上黨東　九域志今潞州有上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='586:591'>　黨河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='591:614'>　雷首山　水經雷首山在河東蒲坂縣東南南有厯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='614:637'>　山舜所耕處又曰伯夷叔齊隐于首陽山馬融曰在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='637:660'>　蒲坂華山之北河曲之中揚雄河東賦曰登厯觀而</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='660:683'>　逺望兮聊浮㳺于河之巖注雷首西枕大河　九域</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='683:706'>　志雷首山今在陝州陝音閃中从兩入與陜字不同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='706:732'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-2b' );" name="003-2b" class="pb">[003-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='732:755'>　陜音狎中从兩人　郭縁生述征記云華山與首陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='755:778'>　本同一山河神巨靈擘開以通河流　九域志今河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='778:800'>　中府有巨靈祠有夷齊廟或謂首陽即雷首未詳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='800:823'>　太岳山　水經太岳山在河東永安縣山即冀州岳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='823:846'>　陽也　周禮職方氏冀州山鎮曰霍山即霍太山也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='846:853'>　亦曰太岳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='853:876'>　厎柱山　水經厎柱山在河東太陽縣東河中　顔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='876:895'>　師古曰在陜縣東北山在河中形若柱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='895:921'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-3a' );" name="003-3a" class="pb">[003-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='921:941'>　析城山　水經析城山在河東濩澤縣西南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='941:964'>　王屋山　水經王屋山在河東垣曲縣東北昔黄帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='964:987'>　受丹訣于是山所謂河東者西河之東也厎柱山在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='987:1001'>　東河中又東至于厎柱是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='1001:1024'>　太行山　水經太行山在河内野王縣西北注太行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='1024:1048'>　山一名歸山王烈得石髓處也　馮衍𫝊注太行山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1048:1071'>　在上黨南　九域志今河東路龍徳府潞州有上黨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1071:1094'>　縣河北西路懷州有太行山河東路澤州亦有太行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1094:1120'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-3b' );" name="003-3b" class="pb">[003-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1120:1134'>　山顔師古在河内山陽西北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1134:1157'>　恒山　水經恒山為北嶽在中山郡上曲陽縣西北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1157:1180'>　碣石山　解在冀州　顔師古註漢地理志曰太行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1180:1204'>　恒山二山連延東北接碣石而入于海與孔氏書𫝊</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1204:1227'>　同　漢武帝元封元年行自泰山東廵海上至碣石</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1227:1250'>　文穎曰碣石在遼西絫縣縣今罷屬臨榆此石著海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1250:1273'>　旁顔師古曰碣者碣然特立之貎也　經言夾右碣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1273:1296'>　石鄭康成以為禹由碣石山西北行盡冀州之境還</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1296:1322'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-4a' );" name="003-4a" class="pb">[003-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1322:1345'>　從山東南行入河　正義云鄭以北行則東為右南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1345:1365'>　行西為右故夾山兩旁山常居右與孔傳異</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1365:1388'>　三條四列　按尚書正義導岍至敷淺原舊説以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1388:1411'>　三條地里志云禹貢北條荆山在馮翊懷徳縣南南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1411:1434'>　條荆山在南郡臨沮縣東北此是舊有三條之説馬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1434:1457'>　融王肅皆以為三條導岍為北條西傾為中條嶓冢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1457:1480'>　為南條鄭康成以為四列謂導岍為正陰列西傾為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1480:1503'>　次陰列嶓冢為次陽列岍山為正陽列其首尾延連</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1503:1529'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-4b' );" name="003-4b" class="pb">[003-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1529:1544'>　相及孔氏之意亦必與馬鄭同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1544:1566'>西傾朱圉鳥鼠至于太華熊耳外方桐柏至于陪尾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1566:1577'>　西傾山　解在梁州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1577:1600'>　朱圉山　水經朱圉山在天水北冀縣南山有石鼓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1600:1623'>　開山圖謂之天鼓山　顔師古曰朱圉山在漢陽冀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1623:1628'>　縣南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1628:1639'>　鳥鼠山　解在雍州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1639:1662'>　太華山　在京兆華陰縣南　山海經曰太華之山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1662:1688'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-5a' );" name="003-5a" class="pb">[003-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1688:1711'>　削成而四方其髙五千仭其廣十里鳥獸莫居有蛇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1711:1734'>　焉名曰肥遺方足四翼見則天下大旱武王放馬牛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1734:1758'>　于桃林墟孔安國曰在華山東屬漢𢎞農郡華陰縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1758:1781'>　　書疏華山四州之際東北冀東南豫西南梁西北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1781:1804'>　雍十字分之四隅為四州一名太華　水經注引國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1804:1827'>　語云華岳本一山當河河水過而曲行河神巨靈手</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1827:1850'>　盪脚蹋開而為兩今掌足之跡仍存華巖開山圖曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1850:1873'>　有巨靈者偏得神元之道能造山川出河所謂巨靈</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1873:1899'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-5b' );" name="003-5b" class="pb">[003-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1899:1922'>　贔屭首戴靈山者也　顔師古曰太華即今華陽山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1922:1939'>　　九域志華州潼闗即桃林之塞也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1939:1963'>　熊耳山　在𢎞農盧氏縣東　水經注熊耳山一名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1963:1986'>　蔓渠　山海經曰其上多漆其下多椶餘豪之水出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1986:2009'>　焉西北流注于洛洛水之北有熊耳山雙巒競舉狀</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='2009:2032'>　同熊耳注曰此自别山不與禹貢導洛自熊耳同也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2032:2055'>　昔漢光武破赤眉樊崇積甲仗與熊耳山平即是南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2055:2072'>　安縣有熊耳峽　顔師古曰在陜東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2072:2098'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-6a' );" name="003-6a" class="pb">[003-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2098:2121'>　外方山　即嵩髙山也在潁川　水經外方山崧髙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2121:2144'>　是也　鄭康成毛詩譜云外方之山即嵩髙也山海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2144:2168'>　經謂為大室之山左𫝊司馬侯言大室杜預曰在河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2168:2191'>　南陽城縣西南　孟子益避禹之子于箕山之陰注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2191:2214'>　云嵩髙之北　漢地理志崈髙縣屬潁川郡武帝置</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2214:2237'>　以奉大室山是為中岳有大室中室山廟古文以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2237:2260'>　外方山崈古崇字顔師古曰外方在潁川故縣即崇</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2260:2265'>　髙也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2265:2291'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-6b' );" name="003-6b" class="pb">[003-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2291:2311'>　桐柏山　水經桐柏山在南陽平氏縣東南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2311:2334'>　陪尾山　水經陪尾山在江夏安陸縣東北　泗水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2334:2357'>　注魯國卞縣東南陶虚西阜泗水出焉博物志曰泗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2357:2380'>　出陪尾即斯阜也此自是魯國泗水之所出俗呼媯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2380:2403'>　亭山偶名陪尾非安陸之陪尾山也　漢地理志安</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2403:2426'>　陸縣横尾山在東北古文以為倍尾山倍讀曰陪顔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2426:2449'>　師古曰熊耳外山桐柏陪尾四山相連也　晉地理</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2449:2470'>　志江夏郡安陸縣横尾山在東北古之陪尾山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2470:2496'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-7a' );" name="003-7a" class="pb">[003-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2496:2511'>導嶓冢至于荆山内方至于大别</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2511:2535'>　嶓冢山　解在梁州　水經穀水出𢎞農黽池縣南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2535:2558'>　嶓冢林穀陽谷注山海經曰傅山之西有林焉曰嶓</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2558:2581'>　冢穀水出焉東流注于洛今穀水出于崤東馬頭山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2581:2604'>　穀陽谷東北流厯黽池川漢景帝三年初徙萬户為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2604:2627'>　因崤黽之池以目縣焉此非漾水所出之嶓冢山乃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2627:2646'>　嶓冢林耳嶓冢山在隴西詳在導川漾水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2646:2669'>　荆山　此梁州荆山在梁荆二州之間故晉志謂荆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2669:2695'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-7b' );" name="003-7b" class="pb">[003-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2695:2718'>　州取名于荆山　水經荆山在南郡臨沮縣東北注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2718:2741'>　南條山也卞和得璞玉于是山楚王不理懷玉哭于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2741:2764'>　其下後玉人理之所謂和氏之璧　荆州記曰西北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2764:2787'>　三十里有清谿谿即荆山首曰景山即卞和泣玉處</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2787:2807'>　南郡賦曰漢水至荆山東别流為滄浪之水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2807:2830'>　内方山　水經内方山在江夏竟陵縣東北　漢地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2830:2850'>　理志竟陵縣章山在東北古文以為内方山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2850:2873'>　大别山　水經大别山在廬江安豐縣西南漢水觸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l133' data-llen='2873:2899'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-8a' );" name="003-8a" class="pb">[003-8a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l134' data-llen='2899:2923'>　大别山而南入于江　左𫝊定公四年呉伐楚楚子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l135' data-llen='2923:2946'>　常濟漢而陳自小别至于大别二别皆在漢上杜預</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l136' data-llen='2946:2969'>　曰禹貢漢水至大别南入江然則此二别在江夏界</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l137' data-llen='2969:2992'>　　水經注曰巴水出雩婁縣之下靈山即大别山也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l138' data-llen='2992:3014'>　與決水同出一山故世謂之分水山亦或曰巴山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l139' data-llen='3014:3037'>　京相璠春秋土地名曰大别漢東山名也在安豐縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l140' data-llen='3037:3060'>　南杜預釋地曰二别近漢之名無縁乃在安豐案地</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l141' data-llen='3060:3083'>　説言漢水東行觸大别之陂南與江合則與禹貢相</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l142' data-llen='3083:3109'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-8b' );" name="003-8b" class="pb">[003-8b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l143' data-llen='3109:3114'>　符矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l144' data-llen='3114:3132'>岷山之陽至于衡山過九江至于敷淺原</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l145' data-llen='3132:3155'>　岷山　解在梁州　漢地理志作㟭郊祀志云瀆山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l146' data-llen='3155:3178'>　蜀之岷山也秦漢時又謂之瀆山始皇常令祠官奉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l147' data-llen='3178:3201'>　祠　王羲之與謝安書曰蜀中山川如岷山夏含霜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l148' data-llen='3201:3224'>　雪攷之前聞崑崙之中也　九域志成都府路茂州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l149' data-llen='3224:3230'>　有岷山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l150' data-llen='3230:3253'>　衡山　水經衡山在長沙湘南縣東南注禹治洪水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l151' data-llen='3253:3279'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-9a' );" name="003-9a" class="pb">[003-9a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l152' data-llen='3279:3302'>　至此祭衡山于是得金簡玉字之書案省玉字得通</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l153' data-llen='3302:3323'>　水理也　顔師古曰岷山江所出衡山江所經</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l154' data-llen='3323:3347'>　敷淺原　水經敷淺山地在豫章歴陵縣西南有傅陽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l155' data-llen='3347:3371'>　山即敷淺原　漢志敷淺原一名傅昜山在豫章郡歴</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l156' data-llen='3371:3395'>　陵縣傅昜川在南顔師古曰傅讀曰敷昜古陽字　今</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l157' data-llen='3395:3419'>　觀所謂傅昜山甚庳小恐非經所記者或謂衡山東至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l158' data-llen='3419:3443'>　廬阜極于大江彭蠡之交而止疑此為敷淺原白居易</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l159' data-llen='3443:3466'>　以為江入海處為敷淺原則丹陽京口之間殆非也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l160' data-llen='3466:3492'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-9b' );" name="003-9b" class="pb">[003-9b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l161' data-llen='3492:3507'>導弱水至于合黎餘波入于流沙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l162' data-llen='3507:3530'>　導川　弱水　弱水西至酒泉合黎張掖郡居延縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l163' data-llen='3530:3553'>　東北有居延澤即流沙河也　水經合離山在酒泉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l164' data-llen='3553:3576'>　㑹水縣東北注云即合黎山也　後漢張掖居延屬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l165' data-llen='3576:3599'>　前漢張掖郡居延縣居延國有居延澤古流沙獻帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l166' data-llen='3599:3622'>　建安末立為西海郡澤在東北古文以為流沙王莽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l167' data-llen='3622:3645'>　改曰居成　漢地理志合黎作合藜顔師古曰流沙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l168' data-llen='3645:3668'>　在燉煌西　孔氏傳合黎水名顧氏謂水與山合因</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l169' data-llen='3668:3695'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-10a' );" name="003-10a" class="pb">[003-10a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l170' data-llen='3695:3701'>　山為名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l171' data-llen='3701:3724'>導河積石至于龍門南至于華陰東至于厎柱又東至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l172' data-llen='3724:3747'>于孟津東過洛汭至于大伾北過洚水至于大陸又北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l173' data-llen='3747:3760'>播為九河同為逆河入于海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l174' data-llen='3760:3783'>　河水　水經崑崙墟在西北去嵩髙五萬里地之中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l175' data-llen='3783:3806'>　也河水出其東北陬屈從其東南流入于渤海又出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l176' data-llen='3806:3829'>　海外南至積石山下有石門河水冒以西南流　山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l177' data-llen='3829:3852'>　海經崑崙墟在西北河水出其東北隅　爾雅河出</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l178' data-llen='3852:3879'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-10b' );" name="003-10b" class="pb">[003-10b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l179' data-llen='3879:3902'>　崑崙墟色白所渠并千七百一川色黄百里一小曲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l180' data-llen='3902:3925'>　千里一曲一直　物理論曰河色黄者衆川之流蓋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l181' data-llen='3925:3948'>　濁之也　酈道元注水經引山海經曰河水出渤海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l182' data-llen='3948:3971'>　又海水西北入禹所導積石山山在隴西郡河闗縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l183' data-llen='3971:3994'>　西南羌中余攷羣書咸言河出崑崙重源潛發淪于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l184' data-llen='3994:4017'>　蒲昌出于海水故洛書曰河自崑崙出于重野謂此</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l185' data-llen='4017:4040'>　矣逕積石而為中國河故成公綏大河賦曰覽百川</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l186' data-llen='4040:4063'>　之洪壯莫尚美于黄河潛崑崙之峻極出積石之嵯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l187' data-llen='4063:4090'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-11a' );" name="003-11a" class="pb">[003-11a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l188' data-llen='4090:4113'>　峨釋氏西域傳曰河自蒲昌潛行地下南出積石郭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l189' data-llen='4113:4136'>　璞云積石山今在金城河門闗西南羌中河水行塞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l190' data-llen='4136:4176'>　外東入塞内<span class='krp-note'>案原本此四句誤作水經在張掖郡/南句下今攷水經及山海經注移正</span>水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l191' data-llen='4176:4199'>　經又云河又東入塞過敦煌酒泉張掖郡南注云河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l192' data-llen='4199:4222'>　自蒲昌有隐淪之證並間闗入塞之始重源發于西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l193' data-llen='4222:4245'>　塞之外出于積石之山禹貢所謂導河自積石也山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l194' data-llen='4245:4268'>　在西羌之中燒當所居也後漢桓帝延熹二年西羌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l195' data-llen='4268:4291'>　燒當犯塞䕶羌校尉段熲討之追出塞至積石山斬</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l196' data-llen='4291:4318'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-11b' );" name="003-11b" class="pb">[003-11b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l197' data-llen='4318:4341'>　首而還司馬彪曰西羌者自析支以西濵于河首在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l198' data-llen='4341:4364'>　右居也河水屈而東北流逕于析支之地是為河曲</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l199' data-llen='4364:4387'>　矣應劭曰禹貢析支屬雍州在河闗之西東去河闗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l200' data-llen='4387:4410'>　千餘里羌人所居謂之河曲羌也東北逕厯敦煌酒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l201' data-llen='4410:4433'>　泉張掖南　案諸書皆言河自崑崙然班固漢書叙</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l202' data-llen='4433:4456'>　張騫奉使西域厯諸國烏覩所謂崑崙蘇氏謂騫徒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l203' data-llen='4456:4479'>　見蔥嶺于闐二水便謂之河不知河在西南羌中吐</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l204' data-llen='4479:4496'>　蕃自言崑崙在國西南河之所出也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l205' data-llen='4496:4523'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-12a' );" name="003-12a" class="pb">[003-12a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l206' data-llen='4523:4546'>　龍門　水經河水又南過河東北屈縣西注云屈縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l207' data-llen='4546:4569'>　故城西十里有風山西四十里河南有孟門山淮南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l208' data-llen='4569:4592'>　子曰龍門未闢吕梁未鑿河出孟門之上大溢逆流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l209' data-llen='4592:4615'>　無有丘陵髙阜滅之名曰洪水大禹疏通謂之孟門</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l210' data-llen='4615:4638'>　穆天子傳曰北登孟門九河之嶝孟門即龍門之上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l211' data-llen='4638:4661'>　口也實謂黄河之巨阨兼孟津之名矣此石經始禹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l212' data-llen='4661:4684'>　鑿河中潄廣夾岸崇深傾崖返捍巨石臨危若墜復</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l213' data-llen='4684:4707'>　倚古之人有言水非石鑿而能入石信哉　水經河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l214' data-llen='4707:4734'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-12b' );" name="003-12b" class="pb">[003-12b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l215' data-llen='4734:4757'>　水又南得鯉魚注厯澗東入窮溪首便其源也爾雅</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l216' data-llen='4757:4780'>　曰鱣鮪也出鞏穴三月則上渡龍門得渡為龍否則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l217' data-llen='4780:4803'>　點額而還　魏土地記曰梁山北有龍門山大禹所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l218' data-llen='4803:4826'>　鑿通孟津河口廣入十步巖際䥴迹遺功尚存岸上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l219' data-llen='4826:4850'>　並有廟祠　司馬遷𫝊遷生龍門顔師古曰龍門山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l220' data-llen='4850:4873'>　其東則在今泰州龍門縣北其西則在今同州韓城</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l221' data-llen='4873:4897'>　縣北而河從其中下流馮衍𫝊注龍門河所經今絳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l222' data-llen='4897:4920'>　州縣也案龍門山有二名隋煬帝營宫洛陽登卬山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l223' data-llen='4920:4947'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-13a' );" name="003-13a" class="pb">[003-13a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l224' data-llen='4947:4970'>　望伊闕曰此豈非龍門邪因謂之龍門非禹貢之龍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l225' data-llen='4970:4992'>　門也伊闕龍門其下有灘名八節灘白居易所開</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l226' data-llen='4992:5015'>　九域志今河中府龍門縣有龍門山書云導河至龍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l227' data-llen='5015:5021'>　門是也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l228' data-llen='5021:5044'>　華陰　水經河水又南至華陰潼闗渭水從西來注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l229' data-llen='5044:5067'>　之注云河在闗内撞激闗山謂之潼闗　又云闗山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l230' data-llen='5067:5090'>　在扶風汧縣之西注云河水自潼闗東北流側有長</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l231' data-llen='5090:5113'>　坂謂之黄卷坂傍絶澗涉此坂以升潼闗所謂泝黃</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l232' data-llen='5113:5140'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-13b' );" name="003-13b" class="pb">[003-13b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l233' data-llen='5140:5163'>　卷以濟潼闗也厯北出東崤通謂之函谷闗邃岸天</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l234' data-llen='5163:5186'>　髙空谷幽深澗道之峽車不方軌號曰天險故西京</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l235' data-llen='5186:5209'>　賦曰巖險周固襟帶易守所謂秦得百二并吞諸侯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l236' data-llen='5209:5213'>　也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l237' data-llen='5213:5236'>　厎柱　水經河水又東過砥柱間注云砥柱山名也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l238' data-llen='5236:5259'>　昔禹治洪水山陵當水者鑿之故破山以通河河水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l239' data-llen='5259:5282'>　分流包山而過山見水中若柱然故曰砥柱也三穿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l240' data-llen='5282:5305'>　既決水流疏分指狀表目亦謂之三門矣山在虢城</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l241' data-llen='5305:5332'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-14a' );" name="003-14a" class="pb">[003-14a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l242' data-llen='5332:5355'>　東北太陽縣城東也　顔師古曰砥柱在陜縣東北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l243' data-llen='5355:5366'>　山在河中形若柱也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l244' data-llen='5366:5389'>　孟津　水經河水又東逕平縣故城北酈注云河南</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l245' data-llen='5389:5413'>　有鉤陳壘世𫝊武王伐紂八百諸侯所㑹處尚書所</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l246' data-llen='5413:5436'>　謂不期同時也紫㣲有鉤陳之宿主鬭訟兵陣故遁</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l247' data-llen='5436:5459'>　甲攻取之法以所攻神與鉤陳并氣下制所臨之辰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l248' data-llen='5459:5482'>　則秩禽敵是以壘資其名河水于斯有盟津之目論</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l249' data-llen='5482:5505'>　衡曰武王伐紂升舟陽侯波起疾風逆流武王操黄</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l250' data-llen='5505:5532'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-14b' );" name="003-14b" class="pb">[003-14b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l251' data-llen='5532:5555'>　鉞而麾之風波畢除中流白魚入于舟燌以告天與</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l252' data-llen='5555:5578'>　八百諸侯咸同此盟故曰孟津亦曰盟津又曰富平</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l253' data-llen='5578:5614'>　津杜預建浮橋于此<span class='krp-note'>案原本此句在孔頴達正/義之後今從水經注移入</span>所謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l254' data-llen='5614:5637'>　造舟為梁又謂之陶河昔禹治洪水觀于河見白面</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l255' data-llen='5637:5660'>　長人魚身出曰吾河精也授禹河圖而還于淵及周</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l256' data-llen='5660:5683'>　王子朝篡位與敬王戰乃取周之寶玉沈河以祈福</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l257' data-llen='5683:5706'>　後二日津人得之河上將賣之則變而為石及敬王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l258' data-llen='5706:5729'>　位定得玉者獻之復為玉也　顔師古曰孟津在洛</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l259' data-llen='5729:5756'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-15a' );" name="003-15a" class="pb">[003-15a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l260' data-llen='5756:5779'>　陽之北都道所凑故號孟津孟長大也漢地理志作</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l261' data-llen='5779:5802'>　盟音同孔安國曰孟地名在洛北都道所凑古今以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l262' data-llen='5802:5825'>　為津俗謂之治戌津今河陽縣津也　孔穎達曰孟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l263' data-llen='5825:5848'>　地名津是所渡處水河流至此其勢稍緩可以横舟</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l264' data-llen='5848:5868'>　而渡武王伐商渡師于此後世謂之武濟水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l265' data-llen='5868:5891'>　洛汭　水經河水又東泲水入焉洛水從縣西北流</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l266' data-llen='5891:5914'>　注之注云洛水于鞏縣而東洛汭北對琅琊渚入于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l267' data-llen='5914:5937'>　河謂之洛口自縣西來而北流注洛清濁異流皦焉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l268' data-llen='5937:5964'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-15b' );" name="003-15b" class="pb">[003-15b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l269' data-llen='5964:5987'>　殊别應瑒靈河賦曰資靈川之遐源出崑崙之神丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l270' data-llen='5987:6010'>　涉津洛之峻泉播九道于中州山海經曰洛水成臯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l271' data-llen='6010:6033'>　西入河是也謂之洛汭即什谷也故張儀説秦曰下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l272' data-llen='6033:6056'>　兵三川塞什谷之口謂此水也史記音義曰鞏縣有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l273' data-llen='6056:6079'>　鄩谷水　河至孟津又東行及鞏縣東洛自西南來</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l274' data-llen='6079:6096'>　入之河自洛北過之故曰東過洛汭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l275' data-llen='6096:6119'>　大伾　水經河水又東過成臯縣北濟水從北來注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l276' data-llen='6119:6142'>　之又東逕成臯大伾山下　爾雅釋山曰山一成伾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l277' data-llen='6142:6169'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-16a' );" name="003-16a" class="pb">[003-16a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l278' data-llen='6169:6192'>　許叔重吕忱並以為一成也孔安國以為再成曰伾</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l279' data-llen='6192:6215'>　亦或以為地名鄭康成曰地喉也沇出伾際然則大</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l280' data-llen='6215:6238'>　伾在河内修武武徳之界濟沇之水與滎播澤出入</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l281' data-llen='6238:6261'>　自此然則大伾即是山矣伾北即經所謂濟水從北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l282' data-llen='6261:6284'>　來注之者也伾備悲反爾雅作坯音同在今通利軍</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l283' data-llen='6284:6307'>　　顔師古注地理志山再重曰坯音平鄙反張晏曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l284' data-llen='6307:6330'>　成臯縣山是也薛瓚以為今修武武徳無此山也成</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l285' data-llen='6330:6353'>　臯縣山又不一成也今黎陽山臨河豈是乎師古以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l286' data-llen='6353:6380'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-16b' );" name="003-16b" class="pb">[003-16b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l287' data-llen='6380:6392'>　為在成臯溝洫志注同</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l288' data-llen='6392:6415'>　洚水　水經河水又東北逕元城縣故城西北而至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l289' data-llen='6415:6438'>　沙丘堰注云元城縣北有沙丘堰者不遵其道曰降</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l290' data-llen='6438:6461'>　亦曰潰堰障水即降水也顔師古以為在信都　洚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l291' data-llen='6461:6484'>　水一名濁漳水水經濁漳水出上黨長子縣西發鳩</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l292' data-llen='6484:6507'>　之山漳水出焉東過其縣南屈從其縣東北流注又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l293' data-llen='6507:6530'>　東過壺闗縣北又東北過屯留縣潞縣北注闞駰曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l294' data-llen='6530:6553'>　潞縣有潞水為冀州浸即漳水也世人謂濁漳為潞</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l295' data-llen='6553:6580'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-17a' );" name="003-17a" class="pb">[003-17a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l296' data-llen='6580:6603'>　水又東過武安縣又東出山過鄴縣西又東過列人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l297' data-llen='6603:6626'>　縣南又東北過斥漳縣南又東北過曲周縣東又東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l298' data-llen='6626:6649'>　北過鉅鹿縣東又北過堂陽縣西又東北過扶柳縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l299' data-llen='6649:6672'>　北又東北過信都縣西又東北過下博縣西又東北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l300' data-llen='6672:6695'>　過阜城縣北又東北至昌亭與雽池河會酈道元注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l301' data-llen='6695:6718'>　云漳水又東北逕武邑縣郭南又東逕武强縣北又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l302' data-llen='6718:6741'>　東逕武隧縣故城南白馬河注之水上承雽池東逕</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l303' data-llen='6741:6764'>　樂昌縣北饒陽縣南又東南逕武邑縣北而東入衡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l304' data-llen='6764:6791'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-17b' );" name="003-17b" class="pb">[003-17b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l305' data-llen='6791:6814'>　水謂之交津口又云衡漳又東逕武邑縣故城北又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l306' data-llen='6814:6837'>　東北右合張平口故溝上承武强淵又逕東昌縣故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l307' data-llen='6837:6860'>　城北又東北左㑹滹池故瀆謂之合口又東北分為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l308' data-llen='6860:6883'>　二川當其水決處名之曰李聰渙又東北至樂成陵</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l309' data-llen='6883:6906'>　縣别出北又東北過成平縣南又東北過章武縣西</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l310' data-llen='6906:6929'>　又東北過平舒縣南東入海　案漳水與荆州漳水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l311' data-llen='6929:6952'>　不同左傳江漢沮漳楚之望也此荆州之漳非冀州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l312' data-llen='6952:6972'>　之漳也又洛州又有衡漳則此水之所經也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l313' data-llen='6972:6999'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-18a' );" name="003-18a" class="pb">[003-18a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l314' data-llen='6999:7022'>　大陸　在鉅鹿縣北解在冀州　水經沙丘堰至于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l315' data-llen='7022:7045'>　大陸北播為九河注云風俗通河播也播為九河自</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l316' data-llen='7045:7050'>　此始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l317' data-llen='7050:7073'>　九河逆河　鄭康成曰九河下尾合曰逆河言相承</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l318' data-llen='7073:7096'>　受也蓋所洄下之勢以通河海及齊威霸世塞廣田</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l319' data-llen='7096:7119'>　居同為一河故自堰以北舘陶貝丘鬲盤廣川信都</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l320' data-llen='7119:7142'>　東光河間樂成以東城地並存川瀆多亡漢世河決</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l321' data-llen='7142:7165'>　金堤南北離其害議者常欲求九河故迹而川之未</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l322' data-llen='7165:7192'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-18b' );" name="003-18b" class="pb">[003-18b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l323' data-llen='7192:7215'>　知其所是以班固云自兹距漢北亡八枝者也　漢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l324' data-llen='7215:7238'>　地理志顔師古曰播布也同合也九河又合而為一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l325' data-llen='7238:7261'>　名為逆河言相迎受也海即渤海也　溝洫志河災</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l326' data-llen='7261:7284'>　之羡溢害中國也尤甚唯是為務故導河自積石厯</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l327' data-llen='7284:7307'>　龍門南到華陰東下底柱孟津雒汭至于大伾于是</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l328' data-llen='7307:7330'>　禹以為河所從來者髙水湍悍難以行平地數為敗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l329' data-llen='7330:7353'>　迺釃二渠以引其河北載之髙地過洚水至于大陸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l330' data-llen='7353:7376'>　播為九河同為逆河入于渤海孟康曰禹釃二渠其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l331' data-llen='7376:7403'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-19a' );" name="003-19a" class="pb">[003-19a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l332' data-llen='7403:7426'>　一出貝丘西南南折者也其一則漯川也河自王莽</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l333' data-llen='7426:7449'>　時遂空唯用漯耳薛瓚以為禹貢夾右碣石入于河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l334' data-llen='7449:7472'>　則河入海乃在碣石也武帝元光二年河移徙東都</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l335' data-llen='7472:7495'>　更注渤海禹時不注也　漢武帝元光二年河徙東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l336' data-llen='7495:7518'>　郡更注渤海司空掾王横言曰徃昔天嘗連北風海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l337' data-llen='7518:7541'>　水溢西南出浸數百里故張揖云碣在海中蓋淪于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l338' data-llen='7541:7564'>　海水也昔燕齊遼曠分置營州今城届海濵海水北</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l339' data-llen='7564:7587'>　浸城垂淪半王横之言信而有徴　説者謂九河之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l340' data-llen='7587:7614'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-19b' );" name="003-19b" class="pb">[003-19b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l341' data-llen='7614:7637'>　名初無意義孫炎郭璞李廵從而為之説率多附㑹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l342' data-llen='7637:7660'>　孔穎達謂經言九河既道謂復其故道則名應先有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l343' data-llen='7660:7683'>　不是因禹立名如徒駭太史之説也曽氏以為簡絜</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l344' data-llen='7683:7706'>　乃一枝河之名共為八枝其一不名者河之經流也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l345' data-llen='7706:7729'>　先儒不知經流不名乃分簡絜為二以足九數豈有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l346' data-llen='7729:7752'>　七皆複名而簡絜乃單名乎漢許商則以徒駭為本</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l347' data-llen='7752:7775'>　道其八為支流林少穎以為播為九河支派並列其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l348' data-llen='7775:7798'>　勢則均豈一為經流八為支派哉許商上言于成帝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l349' data-llen='7798:7825'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-20a' );" name="003-20a" class="pb">[003-20a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l350' data-llen='7825:7848'>　時謂徒駭在北鬲津在南其間相去三百餘里今徒</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l351' data-llen='7848:7871'>　駭胡蘇鬲津在成平東光鬲縣界中孔穎達謂商言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l352' data-llen='7871:7894'>　三河在三縣界則徒駭在成平胡蘇在東光鬲津在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l353' data-llen='7894:7917'>　鬲縣既分三河之處則太史馬頰覆鬴三者在東光</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l354' data-llen='7917:7940'>　之北成平之南簡絜鉤盤在東光之南鬲縣之北可</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l355' data-llen='7940:7963'>　知　皇朝太宗時參知政事張洎上奏曰昔大禹鑿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l356' data-llen='7963:7986'>　河自積石至于大伾即今成臯縣也或云黎陽山也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l357' data-llen='7986:8009'>　禹以大河流泛中國為害最甚乃于頓丘郡疏二渠</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l358' data-llen='8009:8036'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-20b' );" name="003-20b" class="pb">[003-20b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l359' data-llen='8036:8059'>　以分水勢一渠自武陽縣東引入漯水其東北流至</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l360' data-llen='8059:8082'>　千乘縣入海即今黄河是也一渠疏畎引傍西山以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l361' data-llen='8082:8105'>　東北勢髙壤敞束水勢不使流鑿夾右碣石入于渤</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l362' data-llen='8105:8128'>　海書所謂北過洚水至于大陸降水即濁漳大陸則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l363' data-llen='8128:8151'>　邢州鉅鹿也播為九河同為逆河者河自魏郡貴鄉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l364' data-llen='8151:8174'>　縣分為九道下至滄州合為一河言逆河者謂與海</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l365' data-llen='8174:8197'>　水反覆相承受也齊威公之霸也塞以廣田居惟一</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l366' data-llen='8197:8220'>　河存焉今見冀東界王莽枯河是也洎言詳實唯以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l367' data-llen='8220:8247'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-21a' );" name="003-21a" class="pb">[003-21a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l368' data-llen='8247:8270'>　碣石海為今渤海誤耳　九河雖無異名然其地亦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l369' data-llen='8270:8293'>　多同異漢志滹沱河名曰徒駭則非載籍所著蓋滹</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l370' data-llen='8293:8316'>　沱源流别是一水與禹河不相干滹沱出鎮州逕深</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l371' data-llen='8316:8339'>　定二州之間過瀛霸至莫州入海非與禹河同道也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l372' data-llen='8339:8362'>　樂史寰宇記徒駭在清池縣南鬲津在樂陵縣西東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l373' data-llen='8362:8385'>　北流入饒安縣南入海胡蘇在饒安無棣臨津三縣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l374' data-llen='8385:8408'>　臨津即漢之東光馬頰在樂陵縣東南輿地記所謂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l375' data-llen='8408:8431'>　篤馬河是也一曰在滴河縣北一曰在蓨縣鉤盤在</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l376' data-llen='8431:8458'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-21b' );" name="003-21b" class="pb">[003-21b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l377' data-llen='8458:8481'>　樂陵縣東南一曰在陽信縣北元和志鬲津在安徳</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l378' data-llen='8481:8504'>　將陵縣南馬頰在安徳平原縣南杜佑通典馬頰覆</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l379' data-llen='8504:8527'>　鬴同在安徳縣説者以為碣石在平州正南滄州東</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l380' data-llen='8527:8550'>　北而王横張揖酈道元則以為九河已在海中諸説</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l381' data-llen='8550:8573'>　離析如此至若導河積石本無異説而元和志乃有</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l382' data-llen='8573:8596'>　大積石小積石兩山在其西南羌中首受于闐河派</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l383' data-llen='8596:8619'>　而為之源者為大積石吐谷渾又有柏海河源李道</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l384' data-llen='8619:8642'>　宗自其王庭行空荒二千餘里至柏海僅得逺望積</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l385' data-llen='8642:8669'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-22a' );" name="003-22a" class="pb">[003-22a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l386' data-llen='8669:8692'>　石覽河源而還小積石在河鄯之間玉門陽闗之内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l387' data-llen='8692:8715'>　或謂禹迹不應如是之近當以大積石為導河之始</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l388' data-llen='8715:8738'>　且百川之大無如江河江之所導不過岷山未嘗逺</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l389' data-llen='8738:8761'>　入西域河源乃深跨羌戎絶迹之地况經言導河積</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l390' data-llen='8761:8784'>　石至于龍門積石雖在金城之西龍門乃近華陰中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l391' data-llen='8784:8807'>　間經涉靈夏綏銀以北一二千里皆所不叙聖人行</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l392' data-llen='8807:8830'>　所無事大抵如此説者乃夸詫曠邈以為廣大而不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l393' data-llen='8830:8853'>　知其流于荒誕不經也然九河之説地雖不同而名</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l394' data-llen='8853:8880'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-22b' );" name="003-22b" class="pb">[003-22b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l395' data-llen='8880:8903'>　猶不異至若九江則名亦不一張須元所記已異于</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l396' data-llen='8903:8926'>　張僧監㝷陽記而賈耽又謂江有八洲與江為九如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l397' data-llen='8926:8949'>　曰沙曰人曰九江曰葛曰象曰烏曰感曰蚌又與二</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l398' data-llen='8949:8972'>　張不同且既曰八洲與江為九而八洲之中其一又</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l399' data-llen='8972:8995'>　自名九江其不經可知矣况經史皆言水中可居曰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l400' data-llen='8995:9018'>　洲今謂江有八洲則是江中之洲渚爾安得稱九江</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l401' data-llen='9018:9041'>　乎樂史寰宇記李宗諤九江圖皆本于尋陽記唯鄭</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l402' data-llen='9041:9064'>　康成以為九江乃廬江尋陽山溪九小水入江者孔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l403' data-llen='9064:9091'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-23a' );" name="003-23a" class="pb">[003-23a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l404' data-llen='9091:9114'>　穎達主其説抑不思秦置九江郡漢初以為淮南郡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l405' data-llen='9114:9137'>　武帝復為九江其治在淮水之南與壽春對境未嘗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l406' data-llen='9137:9160'>　近江至王莽名豫章為九江則江西淮西皆在境内</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l407' data-llen='9160:9183'>　隋人名尋陽為九江水北為陽尋亦作潯則在尋水</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l408' data-llen='9183:9206'>　之北非江之北也尋水在江北郡又在尋北則近淮</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l409' data-llen='9206:9229'>　矣或以為九江郡在江北近蘄州界者誤也又以為</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l410' data-llen='9229:9252'>　潯亦江之一名者亦誤也其後以武昌柴桑縣與江</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l411' data-llen='9252:9275'>　北同為九江郡既又移治江南為江州因號尋陽實</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l412' data-llen='9275:9302'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1b0008', 'WYG', '003-23b' );" name="003-23b" class="pb">[003-23b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l413' data-llen='9302:9325'>　非本地白樂天為江州司馬作琵琶行直以今江州</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l414' data-llen='9325:9348'>　之江為尋陽江頭其誤尤甚説者引司馬遷登廬山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l415' data-llen='9348:9371'>　以望九江遂以為九江近廬山然則齊威公登跨河</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l416' data-llen='9371:9394'>　龍門山以望江漢豈亦近之耶大抵登髙望逺茍非</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l417' data-llen='9394:9417'>　有大山障蔽雖數千里盡在目中况柴桑本屬武昌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l418' data-llen='9417:9440'>　去洞庭九江不甚逺宜可望也南北大川支派可疑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l419' data-llen='9440:9453'>　者唯九河九江故併論之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l420' data-llen='9453:9462'>　禹貢指南卷三</span><br/>
</p>
